I have the group set to strip attachments, so nobody can share
viruses. If you want to share photos, maybe you could help her set up
a flickr account? That's a great way for photographers(of any level)
to network.

You could also upload an album to our "photos" section here.

Ren
learninginfreedom.com

messages.subject: WooHoo! She has a hobby!
messages.msgSnippet: My oldest daughter has always been a short term kinda girl. She has played 4 instruments, been a writer, and even dabbled in various arts like dance, painting,
messages.messageBody:
My oldest daughter has always been a short term kinda girl. She has played 4
instruments, been a writer, and even dabbled in various arts like dance,
painting, and photography. And (drum roll please)
She is now passionately perusing photography. After putting all of her
savings into an expensive camera, she is obsessed with photography. And
she's great! Here are a few stock photo's she took. What do you think??


Much Love,
Wildflower
